lead_paragraph: Parts of a mutilated body washed up on the sands of Copacabana Beach in Rio de Janeiro on Wednesday, police said, just meters (yards) from where beach volleyball athletes will compete in the upcoming Olympics.

headline.print_headline: Body Parts Wash Ashore Next to Rio Olympic Venue
